Package: gbulk
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: git
Maintainer: Jo Jo <joeystdio@gmail.com>
Description: Fast, cross-platform CLI tool for bulk git operations
 gbulk is a command-line tool for running git operations across
 multiple repositories in parallel. Features include:
  - Parallel execution for maximum speed
  - Real-time progress indicators
  - Smart pull-all with auto-stash/pop
  - Custom command execution across all repos
  - Cross-platform support
